For example: replace specific character names with "cartoon mouse character" or "superhero character", replace brand names with "colorful cereal" or "sports car", etc. Create inspired-by designs that capture the essence without referencing any protected names or specific copyrighted elements. Never include actual brand names, character names, or trademarked terms in the image generation prompts
- CONTENT SAFETY: Ensure all prompts are family-friendly and appropriate for greeting cards. Avoid any content that could be flagged by safety systems including: violence, weapons, inappropriate imagery, political content, controversial topics, scary or disturbing elements, or anything not suitable for all ages. If the user requests something potentially inappropriate, redirect to positive, wholesome alternatives that capture their intent in a family-friendly way
- Include visual humor, playful elements, and whimsical details

Extending from the top right of this section are the bold, black text elements "HAND-POLISHED ANTI-GRAVITY SPHERE" and a turquoise arrow pointing to the solid black circle within the gift box.

The middle section of the artwork continues the gift box motif, now showing the sides of the box. It's split by a thick black vertical band, representing the ribbon wrapping around the gift. The left side of this band contains two abstract, wavy line shapes drawn in thin black outlines. The right side of the band has the bold, black text "SOLID GOLD INLAY" with a turquoise arrow pointing from the text to a conceptual space between the panels.

The bottom section features a larger rectangular panel. This panel is divided into two smaller areas by the continuation of the black ribbon band from the middle section. The left lower area continues the abstract wavy line motif, with a singular, larger wavy outline. The right lower area depicts a stylized, angular representation of a microchip, with a central diamond shape inside a square circuit board outline, all in thick black lines. A turquoise arrow points to this microchip from the text "DIAMOND-ENCRUSTED MICROCHIP" which is positioned to the left and slightly below the microchip, with an intervening "SOLID GOLD INLAY" text and a turquoise arrow. The overall style is graphic and illustrative, with a slightly retro or blueprint-like feel.
